11:18.278 --> 11:19.761
- [laughs]
all right.

11:20.781 --> 11:22.981
Let the savage savings

11:23.083 --> 11:24.282
begin, yeah!

11:24.384 --> 11:26.051
[crowd cheers]
whoo!

11:26.153 --> 11:27.786
Ooh yeah!

11:27.888 --> 11:29.454
Welcome to sears!

11:29.556 --> 11:32.023
Hey, congratulations,
you're in sears.

11:32.125 --> 11:33.992
Enjoy your sears experience.

11:34.127 --> 11:36.261
Savings, beckons
the macho man!

