- Mention what?
- Wrestling.

13:03.099 --> 13:04.199
- Drink.
[both laugh]

13:04.317 --> 13:06.317
- okay, it's like that.

13:06.853 --> 13:08.386
- 200 bucks?

13:08.488 --> 13:10.021
That's almost double
what I was getting with lawler.

13:10.157 --> 13:11.956
I get in good
with this jarvis guy,

13:12.092 --> 13:13.091
boy...
[chuckles]

