- Oh, we're talking
about wrestling again.

14:02.709 --> 14:04.742
[both laugh]
- cheers.

14:04.828 --> 14:06.477
- I'm just gonna leave
the bottle.

14:06.563 --> 14:07.946
[both continue laughing]

