17:49.936 --> 17:51.402
[glasses clink]
[both laugh]

17:53.022 --> 17:55.690
- I haven't laughed
like this in a long time.

17:55.742 --> 17:58.693
- Well, from my recollection,
we had a lot of laughs

17:58.745 --> 18:00.144
together back in hawaii.

18:00.163 --> 18:01.446
- Oh, god.

18:01.481 --> 18:03.698
I miss those days.

18:03.750 --> 18:06.000
Our friends,
my family.

18:06.035 --> 18:08.202
I feel so isolated here.

18:08.254 --> 18:10.321
- You know,
you can always come and stay

18:10.340 --> 18:12.990
with me and randy in florida if
