- Well, good,
because technically, we have to

18:34.731 --> 18:35.980
since I brought up
wrestling again.

18:36.015 --> 18:37.532
[both laugh]
[glasses clink]

18:37.567 --> 18:38.783
- cheers.

18:40.537 --> 18:44.071
- Oh, no, mr. Johnson,
your money's no good here.

18:44.124 --> 18:46.908
I'm a huge fan.
The food's on the house.

18:46.960 --> 18:48.960
- Well, thank you,
my friend.

18:48.995 --> 18:51.362
[chuckles]
you know what?

18:51.381 --> 18:52.747
Why don't you take
that for yourself, then?

18:52.799 --> 18:54.415
- What?
No, I--

18:54.467 --> 18:56.250
- I insist.

18:56.302 --> 18:57.919
Just keep on cheering for me,
all right?

18:57.971 --> 18:59.754
- Absolutely.

18:59.806 --> 19:01.222
Thank you,
mr. Johnson.

19:02.842 --> 19:04.926
- Gotta launder
that racist money,

19:04.978 --> 19:06.377
make it clean again.

